data.description: This large two story home is centrally located off of W.S. Young with easy access to Fort Cavazos, shopping, and dining! Enjoy this spacious home with two living areas, a formal dining room, upstairs loft, and a beautiful back deck! As you walk through the front door on the lower level, you are greeted with high ceilings and a large living space with a fireplace. The kitchen provides plenty of storage space and leads you into a large flex space or formal dining room. The extended master suite provides the new owner with a large bedroom with a sitting area and a bedroom-size master bedroom closet. As you travel upstairs, you will find an additional 3 bedrooms, a loft and a full bathroom with views of the lower level. You do not want to miss out on this spacious beauty!! Schedule your private showing today!
